org.sql: SELECT changesets.* FROM changesets WHERE changesets.repository_id = "$1" AND scmid IN ('64f1f3e89ad1cb57976ff0ad99a107012ba3481d', '4fc55c43bf3d3dc2efb66145365ddc17639ce81e') ORDER BY changesets.committed_on DESC, changesets.id DESC, committed_on DESC
